net.sf.tweety.arg.deductive.semantics.attacks

Class DirectDefeat

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.tweety.arg.deductive.semantics.attacks.DirectDefeat
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Attack

    public class DirectDefeat
extends Object
implements Attack
    This attack notion models the direct defeat relation; A is defeated by B iff there is c in support(A) with claim(B) |- \neg c.
    Author:
    Matthias Thimm
